| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0017 — Recovery Inhibition (darkvault)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3960c1ea-09dc-5d4f-a0a1-5ab293841dd8"
